==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Argas
<hw>Ar"gas</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A genus of
venomous ticks which attack men and animals. The famous Persian Argas,
also called <stype>Miana bug</stype>, is <spn>Argas Persicus</spn>; that
of <geog>Central America</geog>, called <stype>talaje</stype> by the
natives, is <spn>Argas Talaje</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Argean</ent>⟦br⟧
